      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great? This car has been my pride and joy and is in really solid shape for its next owner. It runs super smooth and has plenty of life left for all your daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road today\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
