    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six. This high-compression power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the 'Big Three' have been proactively addressed: rod bearings replaced with WPC-treated shells, the VANOS system overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe reinforced with integrated steel plates. The chassis is tightened with a Bilstein PSS10 coilover kit, providing adjustable damping for superior lateral grip. While the Alpine White paint shows minor road-wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and structural integrity are excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Engine and transmission run well.",
      "price": 31500.0,
