    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented in a striking deep metallic finish, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to provide a premium driving experience. The exterior retains a high-gloss luster with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and free of major curbing. Step inside to a cabin that has been treated with the utmost respect; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a strict regimen of synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service. It starts reliably, shifts seamlessly through all gears, and offers a tight, responsive handling profile. This is a complete package for the discerning driver who seeks a dependable, well-documented vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 36500.0,
